<section class="home-section">
  <div class="prose">
    <h2>Typography</h2>
    <p class="muted">Public Sans — USWDS typeface. Civic, clean, readable.</p>
    <h1>Heading 1 — clamp(1.9rem, 3.5vw, 2.5rem) / 700</h1>
    <h2>Heading 2 — clamp(1.3rem, 2.2vw, 1.65rem) / 600</h2>
    <h3>Heading 3 — 1.05rem / 600</h3>
    <p>Body text — 1rem / 1.65 line-height. The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.</p>
    <p class="lead">Lead text — slightly larger, muted. Used for intro paragraphs.</p>
    <p class="muted">Muted text — secondary information, metadata, captions.</p>
    <p><a href="#">A link in body text</a></p>
    <p><small>Small text — 0.85rem, used in the footer and fine print.</small></p>
  </div>
</section>

