    <h2>The Cobold</h2>
    <p>
      CoCitizen's mascot. Named for the kobold of medieval German mining lore — the mischievous
      underground spirit that miners blamed for the troublesome blue ore (cobalt) that kept
      contaminating their silver. Our cobold is that spirit: technically a pest, actually kind of
      helpful, always carrying USB drives.
    </p>
    <p class="muted">
      Use sparingly and with purpose. Each variant has a natural home — don't put the hacker on
      the about page. All variants are transparent PNGs. Minimum display size: 120px tall.
    </p>
  </div>
